**BACK ON THE MARKET***

**Assumable Mortgage with 2.75% interest rate for qualified buyers SAVE BIG on your monthly payments!***

Welcome Home!

Step into this mid century brick charmer with a brand new look! Fresh paint and beautiful new landscaping will make you the talk of the block. Plenty of space throughout including a family room with a timeless classic design and separate living and dining areas. Updated kitchen countertops with custom backsplash and granite countertops. Step out onto the huge screened patio perfect for entertaining, reading, or just enjoying a quiet evening looking over your new sprawling fully fenced backyard. No HOA so bring your toys!
